OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out at historic manor
OL,4,Chouse in suspected arson attack
OL,6,FAn historic manor house in Devon has
OL,7,Fsuffered "extensive damage" in a
OL,8,Fsuspected arson attack.
OL,10,FSix fire engines were called to
OL,11,FPoltimore House, near Exeter, in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of Tuesday 9 April.
OL,13,FFirefighters were still at the scene
OL,14,Fof the blaze almost 24 hours later.
OL,16,FCrews were dispatched to the Grade II*
OL,17,Flisted building just after 1am,
OL,18,Ffollowing several 999 calls.
