OL,6,FThe Poltimore House Trust, set up in
OL,7,F2000 to preserve the estate, said the
OL,8,Fhouse had suffered "extensive damage"
OL,9,Fin a suspected arson attack.
OL,11,FChair of the trust, Dr Peter
OL,12,FTotterdill, said: "This amazing place
OL,13,Fhas been loved by so many people over
OL,14,Fthe years, and my heart goes out to
OL,15,Fall the many volunteers who have
OL,16,Fworked so hard to protect and restore
OL,17,FPoltimore House.
OL,19,F"I have been at the House all morning
OL,20,Fand am shocked at the scale of the
OL,21,Fdevastation."
