OL,6,FHe added: "I know that many people are
OL,7,Fdistraught by what has happened and we
OL,8,Fare all feeling a deep sense of loss.
OL,10,F"However I have been in touch with
OL,11,Fmany of our Board members and we're
OL,12,Fdetermined to save what we can of this
OL,13,Fimportant part of Devon's heritage,
OL,14,Fand to hold on to our vision of
OL,15,FPoltimore House and Grounds as a place
OL,16,Ffor everyone.
OL,18,F"More than ever, we need everyone's
OL,19,Fhelp to recover from this disaster and
OL,20,Fto move forward with optimism."
